================================================================================
PURPOSE
================================================================================

operator-commons is a shared library for keiailab Kubernetes operators
(mongodb-operator, postgres-operator, valkey-operator). It provides
reusable abstractions for:

- pkg/labels        — common label selector + StandardLabels builder
- pkg/security      — restricted-PSP-compliant SecurityContext helpers
- pkg/networkpolicy — opinionated NetworkPolicy builders (deny-by-default)
- pkg/monitoring    — ServiceMonitor / PrometheusRule helpers (CRD-soft)
- pkg/version       — semver-aware version matrix helpers
- pkg/webhook       — admission webhook setup + cert helpers

This is a library — it does NOT distribute container images, binaries, or
operator manifests on its own.

